OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with some patchy
OL,6,Fmist and fog. Any cloud soon breaking
OL,7,Fup to leave a dry day with some good
OL,8,Fspells of sunshine. Very warm.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA mostly sunny evening then
OL,11,Fremaining dry with long clear spells
OL,12,Fovernight. Some patchy low cloud
OL,13,Fdeveloping in the east.
OL,14,
OL,15,CMonday:FAny early low cloud in the
OL,16,Feast will quickly clear. Otherwise, a
OL,17,Fdry day with plenty of sunshine and
OL,18,Ffeeling very warm again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
